body:
hey!! im opening commissions!!

im doing it as double work since im also studying!!

prices are:

  • icon flat colors: 10$
  • icon full colors: 12$
  • ¾ Body B/W: $12
  • ¾ Body with flat colors: $15
  • ¾ Body full paint: 20$
  • Full body B&W. $19
  • Full body simple colors. $23
  • Full body full color. $26

5$ for extra characters!!

have in consideration that the prices are based in how long does it take me to finish each piece

ill do any kind of art!, except nsfw, biggotry or mechas but i can work with dnd commissions and furries as well!!

if you want to me, my contact email is swagoowagoo@gmail.com

or send me a direct message trought tumblr!!!

it would help me a lot if you can reblog this post since currently i dont have any income to help me out

So, wanna commission me? Neat!!

Here how to do it:

- Send me an e-mail at swagoowagoo@gmail.com

- Give me your name or a nickname.

- Write if you want a sketch\lineart, a coloured drawing, or an uncoloured one and precise whether you want a bust shot or a full body.

- Name the character(s) that you want.

- Give ALL the details of what you want.

- Then give me the nickname you want me to use so I can write ‘’ Commissioned by ______ ‘’

thank you very much for reading
